text: James Richard Garoppolo (born November 2, 1991) is an American football player. He is a super bowl champion. He used to play for the New England Patriots. Now he plays for the Los Angeles Rams. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:American football quarterbacks Category:New England Patriots players Category:San Francisco 49ers players Category:Sportspeople from Illinois Category:People from Arlington Heights, Illinois Category:Living people
